    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Visual works comprising tiles or having tiles applied as the primary medium. For works in which an individual tile is a support for a design or image, use "art tiles (visual works)." Tile works may incorporate decorated tiles or they may comprise tile that is not decorated.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
